msg.msgText: Name Name of the queue manager connection object QueueManagerName The queue manager to connect to ConnectionName Comma delimited list of connections. For a connection name with a port number, specify the port number in parentheses. For example: 10.0.0.127(1415) ChannelName The channel to use while connecting to the MQ queue manager SSLCipherSpec The SSL cipher specification to match the one on the queue manager
